<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c3">{إرم}</span> و <span class="c3">{إرم}</span> فِي تَفْسِيرِ بَعْضِهِمْ: قَبِيلَةٌ مِنْ عَاد.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُحَمَّد:</span> <span class="c2">(إرم)</span> هِيَ فِي مَوْضِعِ خَفْضٍ وَلَمْ تُصْرَفْ؛ لِأَنَّهَا اسْمٌ لِلْقَبِيلَةِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{ذَاتِ الْعِمَاد}</span> تَفْسِيرُ الْحَسَنِ: ذَاتُ الْبِنَاءِ الرَّفِيعِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>